sql:
SELECT
  c.c_customer_id AS customer_id,
  COALESCE(c.c_last_name, '') || ', ' || COALESCE(c.c_first_name, '') AS customername
FROM customer AS c,
  customer_address AS ca,
  customer_demographics AS cd,
  household_demographics AS hd,
  income_band AS ib,
  store_returns AS sr
WHERE
  ca.ca_city = 'Hopewell' AND c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk AND ib.ib_lower_bound >= 32287 AND ib.ib_upper_bound <= 32287 + 50000 AND ib.ib_income_band_sk = hd.hd_income_band_sk AND cd.cd_demo_sk = c.c_current_cdemo_sk AND hd.hd_demo_sk = c.c_current_hdemo_sk AND sr.sr_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk
ORDER BY
  c.c_customer_id
LIMIT 100;
